{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/tools/movielect/","webpackCompilationHash":"1e8be064bae08d49e4c1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"8bc6d185-6958-577e-93dd-fb049702f234","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>电影可以延长我们的生命，但选电影却会浪费我们的时间，这个小程序的出现就是为了解决这个问题。当你想和朋友一起看电影却不知道看什么的时候，就来随机选一部吧。</p>\n<p>小程序的功能很简单，进入之后就会随机给你推荐一部电影，如果不对你的口味可以摇一下手机换一部。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/2b872/overview.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overview\"\n        title=\"overview\"\n        src=\"/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/e2288/overview.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/264cc/overview.jpg 160w,\n/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/f562b/overview.jpg 320w,\n/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/e2288/overview.jpg 640w,\n/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/b3ee8/overview.jpg 960w,\n/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/6c315/overview.jpg 1280w,\n/static/b48d778754f0b84c63efc51a928e1213/2b872/overview.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>当然，为了让你随机选出更符合口味的电影，我给小程序做了筛选功能。你可以先限定一个范围——什么类型以及好于百分之多少同类型的电影——再进行随机选择。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/2b872/filter.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"filter\"\n        title=\"filter\"\n        src=\"/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/e2288/filter.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/264cc/filter.jpg 160w,\n/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/f562b/filter.jpg 320w,\n/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/e2288/filter.jpg 640w,\n/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/b3ee8/filter.jpg 960w,\n/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/6c315/filter.jpg 1280w,\n/static/2cc053e2663ecea23a0c88dbb0cf9ab1/2b872/filter.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果摇出了你喜欢的电影，你可以将它分享给朋友，还可以生成一张电影卡片分享到朋友圈，分享时还可以顺便写一句话。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/2b872/share.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"share\"\n        title=\"share\"\n        src=\"/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/e2288/share.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/264cc/share.jpg 160w,\n/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/f562b/share.jpg 320w,\n/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/e2288/share.jpg 640w,\n/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/b3ee8/share.jpg 960w,\n/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/6c315/share.jpg 1280w,\n/static/f8973999d43ce05a8ac25cb8ede9fc42/2b872/share.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>啥也不说了，喜欢的话扫描上面的小程序码体验一下吧。</p>\n<h3>参考</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4IyqP3jat9dFDDZsnxgpOg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">如果你想看电影，却不知道看什么</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/J9sPbhaNtbUlBuxEKYH5Pw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">「选个电影」小程序船新版本上线啦</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"选个电影小程序","date":"2015/07/28","description":"一个功能极其简单的小程序，摇一摇随机推荐电影，支持生成卡片分享。","color":"#F2C94C","cover":"movielect.jpg","demo":"demos/movielect.jpg","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/tools/movielect/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lists/collecting.design/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"DesignCollecting"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/brain-hole/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"脑洞没边儿"}}}}}